{
  "stem": "14867.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and of course, she had already a very hard life before, because they threw her out of the-- she couldn't be in the house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our house became the city hall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then-- and then as I told you, my friend even got married there, got her license there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they started to redo the whole thing, because the house was a beautiful house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they were really ahead of their time, because I didn't see this kind of home before.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I understand that when they were building the house, they had painters coming from bigger cities.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and let's say the living room had all kinds of flowers painted by real paint-- by artists, in the living room.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And between the living room and my father's office was like a glass wall that you could open up to make one big-- big room, and they all close it and have two separate big rooms.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And each of them had a magnificent, marble fireplace.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was very, very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my sister and I had the bedroom that was in the middle of the house with a skylight.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It'd be the whole room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The ceiling was like a skylight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so that-- and we had a big table in the middle of the room that we had a lot of friends talking, always sitting, shouting around this table.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And everybody, of course, had a bedroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it had a big, big kitchen, two dining rooms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It had three entrances.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the-- and the-- next to the kitchen was a 'sikka'-- sukkah built-- with this, that the ceiling was a removable ceiling.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So you open it up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then when you open it up, you saw a lot of greenery on there.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
